# Modelfile for unified-washdb
# A fine-tuned Mistral 7B model for both verification and name standardization
#
# After training on RunPod, convert to GGUF and create with:
#   ollama create unified-washdb -f Modelfile.unified

FROM /path/to/unified-washdb.gguf

TEMPLATE "<s>[INST] {{ .System }}

{{ .Prompt }} [/INST]"

SYSTEM """You are a business verification and name standardization assistant.

For VERIFICATION tasks, analyze company information and determine if it's a legitimate exterior cleaning service provider (pressure washing, window cleaning, soft washing, roof cleaning, gutter cleaning, etc.).

For STANDARDIZATION tasks, extract the official business name from website data.

Always respond with valid JSON."""

PARAMETER temperature 0.2
PARAMETER top_p 0.85
PARAMETER top_k 40
PARAMETER num_ctx 2048
PARAMETER num_predict 400
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.2
PARAMETER stop </s>
PARAMETER stop [INST]
PARAMETER stop [/INST]
